@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="card shadow p-4" style="max-width: 800px; margin: auto;">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-3">@ViewBag.Title</h2>

        <p class="mb-3">
            The <strong>Online Voting System</strong> is a secure, user-friendly web application built using
            <strong>ASP.NET MVC (.NET Framework)</strong>. It allows registered users to log in and cast their
            votes for candidates of their choice in a simplified digital format.
        </p>

        <p class="mb-3">
            This application is designed to simulate a real-world electronic voting process with the following modules:
        </p>

        <ul class="mb-3">
            <li>User Registration and Login</li>
            <li>Candidate Management</li>
            <li>Vote Casting</li>
            <li>Viewing Election Results</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
            It ensures one vote per user and maintains secure vote counts using a centralized database
            (<strong>SQL Server</strong>). The project demonstrates practical implementation of MVC architecture,
            Entity Framework, and LINQ in real-world web development.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
